title: Jesse Ed Davis - Ululu (1972; 2004) [FLAC]
description:
Jesse 'Ed' Davis (1944-1988) was a Native American guitarist. Not to confuse with the Jazz saxophonist Jesse Davis.


tracklist:


    Red Dirt Boogie Brother
    White Line Fever
    Father On Down The Road
    Sue Me Sue You Blues
    My Captain
    Ululu
    Oh! Susannah
    Strawberry Wine
    Make A Joyful Noise
    Alcatraz 


lineup:

Jesse Ed Davis - guitar, vocals
Albhy Galuten, Larry Knechtel, Mac Rebenack aka Dr. John. Leon Russel, Stan Szeleste - keyboards, organ, piano
Jim Keltner - drums
Donald "Duck" Dunn, Billy Rich, Arnold Rosenthal - bass
Clydie King, Venetta Fields, Merry Clayton - background vocals
